'''Kotoshironushi Shrine'''（事代主神社）は日本の{{ill|Shinto shrine|ja|神社}}。
* {{ill|Kotoshironushi Shrine (Tokushima City)|ja|事代主神社 (徳島市)}} - located in {{ill|Tokushima Prefecture|ja|徳島県}}{{ill|Tokushima City|ja|徳島市}}. * {{ill|Kotoshironushi Shrine (Awa City)|ja|事代主神社 (阿波市)}} - located in {{ill|Tokushima Prefecture|ja|徳島県}}{{ill|Awa City|ja|阿波市}}. En'gyō-shiki inner small shrine. * {{ill|Kotoshironushi Shrine (Naruto City)|ja|事代主神社 (鳴門市)}} - located in {{ill|Tokushima Prefecture|ja|徳島県}}{{ill|Naruto City|ja|鳴門市}}{{ill|Nuyō Town Minamihama|ja|撫養町南浜}}. * {{ill|Kotoshironushi Shrine (Shinkamigoto Town)|ja|事代主神社 (新上五島町)}} - located in {{ill|Nagasaki Prefecture|ja|長崎県}}{{ill|Minamimatsuura District|ja|南松浦郡}}{{ill|Shinkamigoto Town|ja|新上五島町}}. * {{ill|Amagasaki Ebisu Shrine|ja|尼崎戎神社}} - former shrine name was Kotoshironushi Shrine. Located in {{ill|Hyōgo Prefecture|ja|兵庫県}}{{ill|Amagasaki City|ja|尼崎市}}. {{Disambiguation}}
==Related Items== * {{ill|Kotoshironushi|ja|事代主神}}
